#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/dip_solder.rst:2
msgid "DIP 焊点检测（DIP Solder）"
msgstr "DIP Solder Inspection"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/dip_solder.rst:4
msgid "**此页面的用途**"
msgstr "**What this page covers**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/dip_solder.rst:6
msgid "针对插装（DIP）器件的焊点检测，可结合颜色范围与自定义模型。"
msgstr ""
"Solder-joint inspection for DIP (through-hole) components. Combines color-"
"range analysis with an optional custom-trained model."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/dip_solder.rst:8
msgid "**如何进入**"
msgstr "**How to open it**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/dip_solder.rst:10
msgid "模板编辑器中绘制对应 ROI 后，在参数面板中配置该工具的参数。"
msgstr ""
"Draw the corresponding ROI in the Template Editor, then configure the tool's"
" parameters in the parameter panel."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/dip_solder.rst:12
msgid "**操作流程**"
msgstr "**Workflow**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/dip_solder.rst:-1
msgid "模板编辑器中的 DIP 检测元件示例"
msgstr "Example of a DIP inspection component in the Template Editor"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/dip_solder.rst:18
msgid "**参数说明**"
msgstr "**Parameters**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/dip_solder.rst:20
msgid "**DIP 类型（DIP Type）/ 子类型（Sub Type）**：选择 DIP 焊点形态类别。"
msgstr "**DIP Type / Sub Type**: pick the DIP solder-joint category."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/dip_solder.rst:21
msgid "**自定义模型（Custom Model）**：选用为该焊点类型训练的自定义分类模型。"
msgstr ""
"**Custom Model**: select a custom classifier trained for this solder-joint "
"type."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/dip_solder.rst:22
msgid "**置信度阈值（Confidence Threshold）**：模型判定的置信度门限。"
msgstr "**Confidence Threshold**: confidence cutoff used by the model."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/dip_solder.rst:23
msgid "**焊点数量（Solder Count）/ 焊点宽度 (mm)（Solder Width）**：在 ROI 内均分生成焊点子框。"
msgstr ""
"**Solder Count / Solder Width (mm)**: divide the ROI into equal solder-joint"
" sub-frames."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/dip_solder.rst:24
msgid "**桥接宽度 (%)（Bridge Width）**：相邻焊点连锡检测带宽度。"
msgstr ""
"**Bridge Width (%)**: width of the bridge-detection band between adjacent "
"solder joints."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/dip_solder.rst:25
msgid "**启用焊点颜色范围检测（Enable Solder Color Range Criteria）**：开启后按颜色范围辅助判定。"
msgstr ""
"**Enable Solder Color Range Criteria**: when on, the color range serves as a"
" secondary decision input."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/dip_solder.rst:26
msgid ""
"**焊点颜色公式（Solder Color Formula）**：选择 HSV 或三色（Tricolor）公式；选择三色时配置 **三色 X / Y /"
" Z / A** 系数。"
msgstr ""
"**Solder Color Formula**: choose **HSV** or **Tricolor**; when **Tricolor** "
"is chosen, configure **Tricolor X / Y / Z / A** coefficients."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/dip_solder.rst:27
msgid ""
"**焊点颜色中心色调（Solder Color Center Hue）/ 焊点颜色中心饱和度（Solder Color Center "
"Saturation）**：HSV 模式下色相基准点。"
msgstr ""
"**Solder Color Center Hue / Center Saturation**: HSV reference point (HSV "
"mode only)."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/dip_solder.rst:28
msgid ""
"**焊点颜色起始色调（Solder Color Start Hue）/ 焊点颜色结束色调（Solder Color End "
"Hue）**：色相范围的起止角度。"
msgstr ""
"**Solder Color Start Hue / End Hue**: start and end angles of the hue range."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/dip_solder.rst:29
msgid ""
"**焊点颜色起始明度（Solder Color Start Value）/ 焊点颜色结束明度（Solder Color End "
"Value）**：限定有效像素的明度区间。"
msgstr ""
"**Solder Color Start Value / End Value**: brightness band that valid pixels "
"must fall within."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/dip_solder.rst:30
msgid "**焊点颜色有效比率范围（Solder Color Valid Ratio Range）**：焊点颜色有效比例的 OK 区间。"
msgstr ""
"**Solder Color Valid Ratio Range**: the OK valid-ratio band for the solder "
"color."
